loadGeneForID

@Deprecated
public static Gene loadGeneForID(java.lang.String ID)
Deprecated. because not in use

Tries to load the data on a gene from a file. Searches for either an object, XML, or data file (.obj, .xml, .dat, respectively) in the current data directory. Stops after the first such file was found (order: obj, xml, dat). Assumes that all files for gene have the gene's ID as the basic file name, plus the according extension.

Returns null if no such file was found.
